fehd.ADR_TC: 新界元朗朗日路9號形點I二樓2058號鋪

reviews.text: Comfort food but congee is quite salty. Waiters and waitresses are not friendly, no smile.
poor service and expensive. food is just normal or poor standard.

Never ate there because they gave priority to a llarger groups even though we (2) had waited outside for 30 mins. They just kept waiting for 1, then 2, then 3 tables to clear while we waited! Ridiculous practice.

The congee tastes fine but the deep fried fish balls were too salty. But the main reason for giving 2 stars was the sloppy service we've received. They gave us the wrong congee so they took it away, along with our spoon. Came back with the right one but didn't replace the spoon. Also gave us a wrong drink and charged us more for it. Had to change the drink too, and gave us a second, correct bill without taking the first one away. Then someone else came over, took away both bills and gave us the wrong one back. They also forgot about an item that we ordered at the beginning, which we didn't bother to chase. The people there weren't rude or anything, but seriously? So many mistakes when they weren't even that busy? Not coming back to this place again.
Good noodles, mediocre dumplings and veggies.

result.adr_address: 9 Long Yat Rd, Yuen Long, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 9 Long Yat Rd, Yuen Long, Hong Kong
result.name: YOHO MALL I

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

粥品味道比較濃，但合我個人口味，但食完會口渴。。。沒想到粥麵店有三文治及多士，而且超好味！雲吞麵賣相很"企理" ，愛整潔嘅朋友會欣賞。整體價格略偏高。
環境好，但碗麵份量唔夠，一碗午餐不夠飽
“學記麵店”垃圾級雲吞麵，由麵底至雲吞都苦過打仗條命😰。唔駛旨意再來幫襯！😤😡😠之不過水餃撈麵可以一試，奶醬多🍩🍞更係全場最好食😙食品之一👌
叫咗帶子水餃米，嚟到望到三粒水餃似用蝦造嘅水餃，整爛粒餃子揾唔到有帶子，問店員，佢話帶子切碎咗喺餃子裡面，我話揾唔到有帶子喎，蝦就有，佢淨係話切碎咗喺裡面係咁架，之後唔理我！$46仲要加一，$51！早知$38食鮮蝦雲吞麵啦！👿
跟女朋友在yoho這家吃了個下午茶，點的白灼腰肝咬開一片紅，完全沒煮熟。跟男店員說了下，拿過去重煮後本來的腰肝還少了近一半！就放了幾片生菜湊數。服務態度也極差，從頭到尾一句道歉都沒有，以後不會再來了。
